result.formatted_address: 1&2/F California Tower, 30-32 D'Aguilar St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Ignis

reviews.text:
I guess this club is i really liked the dj and the music.  Unfortunately it was a Thursday and it was quite slow . So not that much People. I guess weekends it’s something different when it gets crowded. 

Free Entry !!! 
10 US-Dollar for a drink 
8 Euro for a drink 

It’s cheap for that area
Good service, nice place, average in food. Will back for cocktails next time

Lunch Menu 3 courses $158，選擇幾多元，由早餐Omelette到午餐Pasta至甜品都有，Menu 分別有Power Breakfast, Leaves, Eggs, Carbs, Proteins and Desserts，加入Superfoods元素，煮法健康，做完運動補充Proteins好選擇
 
Omelette
奄列加入Mushroom、Feta(羊芝士)、Barley (大麥)，蛋炒得香滑有芝士香，加上Mushroom
 
Beetroot Tartare
紅菜頭一向係我至愛，加入藜麥、Ricotta，可混合旁邊Salsa verde (義大利莎莎青醬) 味道清新更有層次
 
Chicken with Corn & Spring onion  (+40)
雞肉用雞胸肉，肉質嫩滑juicy，配上我最喜愛栗米，非常完美
 
Pork Loin with Sweet Potato & Peach (+$40)
豬扒燒得香口juicy，脂肪比較少，入口不感油膩，加上烤蕃薯、桃，帶點清新
 
Lemon Tart
Lemon Tart上加上蛋白糖霜(Meringue) 十足對藝術品，入口甜度適中，帶有檸檬柑橘味香氣
 
House Made Ice-cream
自家雪糕有Hazelnut同 Pistachio，香濃細滑，十分推介 
最後一杯香濃咖啡為午餐畫上完美句號

result.adr_address: 30-32 D'Aguilar St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: California Tower

reviews.text: Big tower. Good views on a clear night. Quite expensive but you’d expect that at the top!
Gorgeous rooftop bar, Ce La Vie on the very top floor! Beautiful views of Hong Kong.

Good selection of restaurants from the bottom floor to the top. Or if you want to get your sweat on then I'd highly recommend signing up for the Pure gym - chances are this is the closest one to those working in central. Top floors have pretty great views, particularly towards the south.
There's this bar located at the rooftop called Cest La Vie. A really nice bar to chill at! Love it!
Pure Fitness at California tower is the best gym in town!
